<h3 style="text-align: center;"><span style="text-decoration: underline;">About Lindsay Buroker:</span></h3>
<blockquote>
<h4 style="text-align: center;">Full-time indie fantasy/steampunk author who loves travel, yoga, tennis, and vizslas. Find out more at her <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20130702043700/http://lindsayburoker.com/" onclick="javascript:_gaq.push(['_trackEvent','outbound-article','https://web.archive.org/web/20130702043700/http://lindsayburoker.com']);" target="_blank">blog</a>, check out <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20130702043700/http://facebook.com/LindsayBuroker" onclick="javascript:_gaq.push(['_trackEvent','outbound-article','https://web.archive.org/web/20130702043700/http://facebook.com']);" target="_blank">her official Facebook page</a>, or <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20130702043700/http://twitter.com/GoblinWriter" onclick="javascript:_gaq.push(['_trackEvent','outbound-article','https://web.archive.org/web/20130702043700/http://twitter.com']);" target="_blank">follow her on Twitter</a>!</h4>
<h4 style="text-align: center;"><strong><em>The Emperor&#8217;s Edge</em></strong> (Book 1 in the series) is currently <strong>free</strong> on <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20130702043700/http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B004H1TDB0?ie=UTF8&amp;tag=tortfighandde-20&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=9325&amp;creativeASIN=B004H1TDB0" onclick="javascript:_gaq.push(['_trackEvent','outbound-article','https://web.archive.org/web/20130702043700/http://www.amazon.com']);">Amazon</a>, <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20130702043700/http://www.barnesandnoble.com/w/emperors-edge-lindsay-buroker/1100124962?ean=2940032862024" onclick="javascript:_gaq.push(['_trackEvent','outbound-article','https://web.archive.org/web/20130702043700/http://www.barnesandnoble.com']);">Barnes &amp; Noble</a>, <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20130702043700/http://www.smashwords.com/books/view/31003" onclick="javascript:_gaq.push(['_trackEvent','outbound-article','https://web.archive.org/web/20130702043700/http://www.smashwords.com']);">Smashwords</a>, <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20130702043700/https://itunes.apple.com/us/book/emperors-edge-high-fantasy/id417327229?mt=11" onclick="javascript:_gaq.push(['_trackEvent','outbound-article','https://web.archive.org/web/20130702043700/http://itunes.apple.com']);">Apple</a> and <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20130702043700/http://www.kobobooks.com/ebook/The-Emperors-Edge-high-fantasy-mystery/book-yCjECZCkh0iaQW14XzW5lg/page1.html?s=utd4atn0S06Omz5B31UubQ&amp;r=4" onclick="javascript:_gaq.push(['_trackEvent','outbound-article','https://web.archive.org/web/20130702043700/http://www.kobobooks.com']);">Kobo</a>! (You can read Paola&#8217;s review <a title="The Emperor’s Edge" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20130702043700/http://novelideareviews.com/the-emperors-edge/" target="_blank">here</a>)</h4>
</blockquote>
