<p>Since Lindsay asked for it, here&#8217;s a recommendation: the &#8216;Magnificent Devices&#8217; series by author Shelley Adina. It&#8217;s a nicely paced steampunk adventure series that doesn&#8217;t get bogged down in world building and has strong, interesting female characters (&#8230;wait, this sounds a bit familiar&#8230; where have I read a book like that recently?). The cover art for her books are awesome, too!</p>
